text: KJBB-LP (94.7 FM; Bear Radio) is a terrestrial American low power radio station, licensed to Brownsboro, Henderson County, Texas, United States, and is owned by the Brownsboro Independent School District. ==References== ==External links== JBB-LP JBB-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2015 Category:2015 establishments in Texas Category:Community radio stations in the United States
